        "subheading": "<p><strong>Stone Shapes</strong></p>",
        "title": "<p>Form, Light & Expression</p>",
        "description": "<p>The shape of a gemstone is one of the most defining elements of a piece.<br/></p><p>It influences not only how a stone looks, but how it interacts with light, how it sits on the hand, and how it feels to wear. Each shape carries its own visual language - some soft and organic, others structured and precise.</p>",
        "feature_text": "<p>We see shape as an extension of personal expression - a balance between proportion, character and intention.</p>",
