        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p>What is a Laboratory Grown Diamond?</p>",
        "description": "<p>Laboratory grown diamonds are diamonds created using advanced technology that replicates the natural conditions in which mined diamonds form beneath the earth.</p><p><br/>From a <strong>chemical, physical and optical perspective, they are identical to diamonds</strong>, with any differences imperceptible to the human eye. Mined and laboratory grown diamonds can only be identified by using specialised equipment.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
