        "media_width": "6",
        "content_position": "topLeftSticky",
        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p><em>Traceability & Transparency</em></p>",
        "description": "<p>Traceability remains one of the most complex aspects of both laboratory grown and natural diamonds.</p><p>Once laboratory grown diamonds enter the global market, identifying their exact origin and production conditions becomes challenging.</p><p>At Natalie Marie Jewellery, we apply the same due diligence standards to laboratory grown diamonds as we do to natural diamonds, working only with suppliers who meet our strict requirements.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
    "text_with_media_QKVKmB": {
      "type": "text-with-media",
      "blocks": {
        "image_pLUtmg": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Screen_Shot_2020-06-16_at_9_40_22_pm_600x_2x_progressive_png.webp"
          }
